reviews.review_text:
Set II is outstanding end of Summer Tour 1983 i hope U have as much fun as i did Taping this show back in July '83.... Camped out on the Beach.... you have too hear 'Fire' in Set II.... we moved to a primo spot for the second Set and it really paid-off for the last Set of The Grateful Dead of Summer '83 Tour in Ventura California
#MuchLOVe from #CaliLAND
